      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept vehicle in good overall condition. It presents nicely inside and out, with a clean exterior and interior, though you should expect some normal signs of use and minor cosmetic wear consistent with age and mileage rather than a mint-level finish. It\u2019s a solid, presentable car that should suit a buyer looking for something dependable and attractive without paying top-of-market money.",
