    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Budget-friendly project with classic appeal, this poor-condition example is best suited for someone looking for a fixer-upper, restoration candidate, or parts car. It shows significant wear, age, and needs, and should be expected to require substantial cosmetic and mechanical work before regular enjoyment. That said, it\u2019s an honest starting point for the right buyer who wants an affordable entry into ownership and is ready to put in the effort.",
