      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation value for the right buyer. It shows its age and wear, but it remains an opportunity for someone seeking an inexpensive car for local use, a backup vehicle, or a project. If you want affordable entry-level mobility without a big upfront cost, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car that can still get the job done? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a backup vehicle, or a project to tinker with. It shows its age and has the usual wear you\u2019d expect, but it\u2019s priced accordingly and offers a lot of value for the money. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Turn-key enough to enjoy and honest enough to improve, this is a solid budget-minded driver/project with strong enthusiast appeal. It fires up, runs, and moves out with good mechanical character, offering a usable powertrain, responsive chassis feel, and the kind of straightforward platform that rewards a hands-on owner. Cosmetically it shows its age and would benefit from TLC, but that also makes it a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable entry point without paying collector money. If you want something inexpensive with real potential and a surprisingly stout feel where it counts, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    }
  ],
